		<fixedName>Zsinj's Dominion</fixedName>
		<!-- <factionNameMaker>guy762_NamerFaction_ZsinjStarfleet</factionNameMaker> -->
		<description>The second-strongest Imperial splinter faction, and the one with the highest likelihood of reuniting the Empire under its banner. Ruled under the iron fist of the Grand Moff of the Queli Oversector, Warlord Zsinj has recently emerged as a powerful figure in both the Empire and the galactic underworld. Having worked closely with the mysterious Darth Vader to covertly undermine the efforts of Prince Xizor (favored by Emperor Palpatine), Zsinj now commands great respect from the Imperial Navy and many criminal organizations and pirate gangs alike. Despite his new rival Isard's successful attempt to convince his top lieutenant, Admiral Treuten Teradoc, to betray him and defect with many of his veteran fleets, Zsinj remains a threat to all with a Super Star Destroyer and a still-massive armada of Imperial and Pirate ships at his disposal. Zsinj's newly-developed Raptor Corps has proven capable enough as an infantry force to rival the dreaded Imperial Stormtroopers, and rumors have begun to surface of his construction of a massive shipyard-battlestation capable of producing additional Super Star Destoyers at unprecedented speeds.</description>
		
